Whether it’s fighting for pro-worker trade policies, workforce development, or increasing funding and treatment options for people diagnosed with cancer, 

Roy and I have been able to work together to get things done for Ohioans and Missourians.

.@RoyBlunt once told me in the 30 years we'd worked w/ each other, we’ve agreed on five things.

Then he said: ‘but you know, all five of those are now federal law.’

That’s how you get things done in the Senate - finding common ground.

He will be missed.
